Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:21.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Crona!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:24.08,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:25.29,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:02:14.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:03.56,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Everyone, please have a look at the chart on page 108 of the textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:06.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we briefly talked about this yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:10.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,the study of souls, as shown in this chart, can be divided into several schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:12.23,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's continue to get along, Crona.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here, take a look, Crona...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:23.66,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It won't be scary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:34.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:42.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is everyone being so kind to someone like me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:48.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:50.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Come on, Crona!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:53.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to be doing better, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:03.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, one step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.24,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:08.91,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about this wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:20.26,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.76,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't cool clinging to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.97,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about a fight we lost, then I can get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:27.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.02,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka's working really hard, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time to be fussing over minor details, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:35.94,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, might as well play one game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:41.90,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Pass it here for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:46.87,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a high center of gravity, so lower your hips more,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,and shoot with your shoulders relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.91,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There, give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:51.62,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.84,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should have a party...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.72,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Drying Happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:05.18,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,To Whom do you Shed Tears in the Moonlight Shine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:18.69,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul, thanks for bringing your records.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, is this stuff okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:25.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought funk music because it's easier to get in the mood,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,but it doesn't match the room's ambiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.24,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:32.96,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, play the piano! There's one right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.38,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted to hear it ever since last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.84,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.50,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the washroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.88,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:43.88,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, he can play the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:49.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,When Soul became my partner, he played it for me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:50.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of piece was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a really gloomy and weird piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:58.06,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He went, "This is the kind of person I am."\N and suddenly played the piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:04.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought that his anxiousness made him an interesting guy, so we soon became partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed the chance to hear him play, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.75,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki, get me some more, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:14.91,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You must feel uncomfortable with this noisy bunch, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:22.42,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,A-{\alpha&HFF}Although I'm still not used to it, I-I don't feel uncomfortable...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.55,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Although I'm still not used to it, {\alpha&HFF}I-I don't feel uncomfortable...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:25.38,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Although I'm still not used to it, I-{\alpha&HFF}I don't feel uncomfortable...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:27.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Although I'm still not used to it, I-I don't feel uncomfortable...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:32.97,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's going to run away or anything, so you'll fit in at your own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:37.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you all quiet over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:41.77,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a party, so let's have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:46.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tease Crona!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:50.62,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is? I'm not teasing anyone, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:55.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Crona, if anyone is teasing you, don't hold back and tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:58.88,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kick his ass for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:04.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everyone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.59,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.55,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all friends, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, get me some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:19.77,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Tsubaki-chan cooked this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.02,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it will be to your liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:25.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:46.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Crona, next time, come hang out at our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:50.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's someone with an appetite like Ragnarok's, I'll be glad to cook again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.09,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:53.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Crona!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:54.97,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.18,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:13.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Crona, you should get a partner that can cook delicious food, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:17.20,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my partner, Ragnarok, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.67,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The party was fun, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:23.38,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really simple-minded, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.56,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed you, Crona.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:46.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Medusa-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.69,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You could recognize me even though I look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.66,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's shameful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You've become small just like I did, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:59.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you in Death City?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.87,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see you, Crona.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I was very worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Worried...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.26,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you come to take me back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:12.88,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you are to stay in Shibusen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:15.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue spying like you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.30,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}S-S-Spying...? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:16.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-{\alpha&HFF&}S-Spying...? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:17.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-{\alpha&HFF&}Spying...? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.76,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-Spying...? {\alpha&HFF&}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:19.56,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-Spying...? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:25.56,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be shy. You infiltrated Shibusen to spy on them, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a task that only you can accomplish, Crona.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:33.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There's supposedly a secret vault somewhere in Shibusen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, find that vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.95,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Crona.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:43.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I have friends at Shibusen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:46.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Betraying Shibusen is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:50.42,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll do it for your mother, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.94,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This just got interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:27.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Death City is swirling with madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:30.38,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that something will happen very soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:48.27,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Pon Poko Dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious when you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of the Pon Poko Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're serious? Do you really listen to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:10:00.62,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I always lose when it comes to studying but, for some reason, I feel like I've won something this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:03.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I listen to it because I like it, so leave me be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.54,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Crona?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:11.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to the dorms...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:13.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:21.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's wrong... She seems a little down lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:24.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so? She's always like that, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:34.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it over with and make up your mind already! You're going to make Medusa angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:46.20,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! How's it going, Justin-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:56.09,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit-kun, since I'm wearing a mask, Justin-kun can't read my lips, can he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:59.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you repeat what I say from now on, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to do something so troublesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if he takes the earphones off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:07.02,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Repeat after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:12.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Justin-kun, I called you here today to assign you to a new mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:14.23,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Hold it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a divine message from Shinigami-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:23.20,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Justin, you're here today to take on a new mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.87,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an important mission, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.87,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:36.67,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that pursuing the Kishin is currently assigned to Azusa, because of her extended field of vision, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:40.01,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Azusa is pursuing Kishin, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:43.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't there a limit to using eyes alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:49.64,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I want you to join the pursuit, travel the world, and act as the "legs."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.77,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You're also to join the pursuit, so there will be both "eyes" and "legs."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the "legs."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:58.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Spirit-kun, repeat it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:00.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you say is a mouthful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:01.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:06.95,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:15.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If you, Justin-kun, go around making a ruckus, you might be able to surprise that cowardly Kishin into jumping out of hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.96,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:25.01,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If you, Justin-kun, go around making a ruckus, you might be able to surprise that cowardly Kishin into jumping out of hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:26.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,My, such a marvelous divine message!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I will gladly abide by it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.61,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:36.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:42.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on, it seems to be an off-limits zone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:46.32,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret vault might be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:51.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? If someone sees me in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just tell them that I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:56.88,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Who goes there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.67,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's only Crona...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.72,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is off-limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.93,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:13.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved us, Marie! We were returning to our room, but we got lost on the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.85,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I'm lost, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:20.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It kind of makes you want to do something about Shibusen's structure, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:23.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's fine! Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:25.61,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.75,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:36.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx212.5\fscy307.5\pos(229,578)}2 \Nhours\N later
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:43.38,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you that we took unnecessarily long!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:47.64,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If something troubles you again, don't worry about it and tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lend you a hand... {\alpha&HFF&}except if you ask for directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:50.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lend you a hand... except if you ask for directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.93,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.94,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The staff room is that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:16.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:22.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I'd rather not infiltrate this dangerous place all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:23.84,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eruka...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:27.30,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the location of the vault? You must have a fair guess, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:31.93,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This is impossible... I can't keep doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:34.85,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter if you tell me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Medusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:43.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Crona, you did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:49.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well then, let's give you a different mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Professor Stein doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:57.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see Professor Stein much so I don't know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:02.67,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Marie-sensei is his partner and they're living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:03.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Marie...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:05.17,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:11.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really nice and always concerned about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:14.18,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:20.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we make use of that kindness?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:30.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:29.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Marie-sensei, goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:31.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Marie-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Crona, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:40.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need me for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:46.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... actually... I wanted to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.01,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.67,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:52.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come over to my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:55.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll drink some tea, and talk about it slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:57.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:01.44,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Inside that pen is a listening device.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:05.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Plant it inside Professor Stein's laboratory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.24,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:17.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, this place only has research materials...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:20.96,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to bring those cups and everything else by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:22.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cute cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything's fine as long as you can drink out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:29.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can see that you've added a woman's touch here and there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:32.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If I overdo it too much, Stein will get angry at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.72,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something worrying you, Crona?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:38.85,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:40.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, why isn't there a share for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:47.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ragnarok, you don't have a mouth, yet you can drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I do have one! Of course I can drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:50.94,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:53.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, I'll go pour some for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Crona, now's the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.08,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop hesitating, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:08.42,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFFF}Salt or pepper, put in whatever you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.76,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Salt or pepper, put in whatever you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:11.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it spicy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:12.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,O-{\alpha&HFF&}Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:13.59,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, {\alpha&HFF&}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:14.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:17.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:21.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, shall we carry on with our conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:24.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:34.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:37.87,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:44.50,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You needed some counseling, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:56.01,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,T-thank you, I f-feel much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:18:00.85,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm happy that I was able to talk to you too, Crona.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:04.85,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's already late, so I'll be going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That went smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:12.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Crona!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:19.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Marie-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:27.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This pen is yours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:30.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:38.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, see you! Take care going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:52.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did everything go smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:02.95,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.24,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome home, Stein.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit, ribbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it! I hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.96,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get that woman to swallow it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:11.67,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:16.26,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,We sneaked it into Marie's coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:25.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That snake was imbued with a listening device using Medusa's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:30.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, every time that woman is near Stein, his madness will increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:32.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crona was just here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:34.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eh, what is it this time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:38.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's not used to school yet, so she's worried about a lot of things...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.78,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But she's a really good girl, and a cute one at that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:45.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not suspicious at all, those idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She'll be alright!{\i0}
